@justinmc  I'm wondering whether this this is should be considered as an issue rather than a proposal to distinguish event types. From my understanding controller is expected to be notified when the text changes only and not on focus change (in the user perspective). 

I'm considering this a bug for now, feel free to update the labels as required.

Cc @LongCatIsLooong @chunhtai 


