I tried the code sample with latest master version running on web and desktop platforms and was able to select that scrolls the content and screen properly as below:

https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/1a976bec-fc85-41f9-a842-cc3c707c6006

This issue occurs because the selection is only updated on drag update events, when we scroll with a mouse wheel no events are received. One thing we can try is reacting to mouse wheel events if we were in the middle of selecting. 

The same behavior can be observed using `SelectableText` with some long text that scrolls.

