### Steps to reproduce

1、Place the input box at the bottom of the webview
2、Set resizeToAvoidBottomInet to true or false
3、Give the input box focus and pop up the keyboard.

### Expected results

Make the input box scroll to the visible area

### Actual results

There is no change in the webview

### Code sample

<details open><summary>Code sample</summary>

