This issue happens because `RenderParagraph`s `_SelectableFragments` are being disposed of on rebuild because non-const `WidgetSpan`s are considered new instances and not identical to the old `WidgetSpan`s. Using const `WidgetSpan`s this issue does not happen.

This also happens without `WidgetSpan`s if you use a dynamic string in the same scenario.

This behavior is also observed using `SelectableText.rich` in a similar manner. One difference is that the selection is not lost when using `SelectableRegion`.

```dart
